---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Card from '../components/Card.astro';
---

<Layout title='Welcome to Astro.'>
  <main>
    <video autoplay muted loop id='myVideo' class='absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-screen object-cover z-0'
           poster='/img.webp'>
      <source src='/RedWoman_compressed.mp4' type='video/mp4' />
    </video>
    <section id='hero' class='flex flex-col justify-between items-start'>
      <nav class='flex flex-row justify-between w-full items-center px-5 py-4 z-50'>
        <h1 class='text-white md:text-[44x] text-[28px] leading-[48px] font-medium'>CLAN™</h1>
        <a
          class='bg-white rounded-[50px] md:h-11 h-7 px-4 md:text-xl text-base flex items-center justify-center text-neutral-950'>
          Sign In
        </a>
      </nav>
      <div class='flex flex-col md:justify-end justify-between h-full p-5 z-50'>
        <h3 class='md:text-[88px] text-[48px] leading-tight text-white'>
          growth agency for fashion brands and independent designers
        </h3>
        <div class='flex flex-col md:grid grid-cols-4 gap-4 mt-8'>
          <p class='text-xl text-white leading-tight'>
            10X avg. revenue growth <span class='text-dusty-rose'>of connected brands in the first year of work</span>
          </p>
          <p class='text-xl text-white leading-tight'>
            100× less spending <span class='text-dusty-rose'>on marketing, website, analytics, compared to other ways of building</span>
          </p>
          <p class='text-xl text-white leading-tight'>
            5+ saved years<span class='text-dusty-rose'> of saved time on growth and experiment</span>
          </p>
          <p class='text-xl text-white leading-tight'>
            30%<span class='text-dusty-rose'> less spending on operational management</span>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class='bg-white min-h-screen py-28 px-5'>
      <p class='text-neutral-950 text-xl font-bold leading-tight'>Our vision</p>
      <p class='indent-10 md:text-[44px] text-[28px] leading-tight'>We help brands to earn money, <span
        class='text-neutral-300'>making them independent and scalable in just a couple of </span>
      </p>
      <div class='flex flex-col md:grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 w-full mt-8'>
        <div class='flex md:flex-row flex-col gap-7 bg-[#F8F8F8] p-5 rounded-[20px]'>
          <div class='flex md:flex-col flex-row flex-wrap gap-4 items-start'>
            <div
              class='md:text-xl text-base h-8 px-3 text-red rounded-[40px] bg-red/10 flex items-center justify-center whitespace-nowrap'>
              years of struggle
            </div>
            <div
              class='md:text-xl text-base h-8 px-3 text-red rounded-[40px] bg-red/10 flex items-center justify-center whitespace-nowrap'>
              unprofitable ads
            </div>
            <div
              class='md:text-xl text-base h-8 px-3 text-red rounded-[40px] bg-red/10 flex items-center justify-center whitespace-nowrap'>
              low sales
            </div>
            <div
              class='md:text-xl text-base h-8 px-3 text-red rounded-[40px] bg-red/10 flex items-center justify-center whitespace-nowrap'>
              high commissions
            </div>
            <div
              class='md:text-xl text-base h-8 px-3 text-red rounded-[40px] bg-red/10 flex items-center justify-center whitespace-nowrap'>
              cash gaps
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class='text-red md:text-[28px] text-xl font-medium leading-tight'>
            Fashion is a struggle. <span class='text-[#E1B4A6]'>1% make it through and many remain unrecognised. Influencers are not effective. Even
            big manufacturers are not making enough. We all dominated by retail and marketplaces and their
            commissions.</span>
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class='flex md:flex-row flex-col gap-7 bg-[#F8F8F8] p-5 rounded-[20px]'>
          <div class='flex flex-col gap-4 items-start'>
            <div
              class='md:text-xl text-base h-8 px-3 text-green rounded-[40px] bg-green/10 flex items-center justify-center whitespace-nowrap'>
              growth
            </div>
            <div
              class='md:text-xl text-base h-8 px-3 text-green rounded-[40px] bg-green/10 flex items-center justify-center whitespace-nowrap'>
              fast results
            </div>
            <div
              class='md:text-xl text-base h-8 px-3 text-green rounded-[40px] bg-green/10 flex items-center justify-center whitespace-nowrap'>
              no risks
            </div>
            <div
              class='md:text-xl text-base h-8 px-3 text-green rounded-[40px] bg-green/10 flex items-center justify-center whitespace-nowrap'>
              controllable
            </div>
            <div
              class='md:text-xl text-base h-8 px-3 text-green rounded-[40px] bg-green/10 flex items-center justify-center whitespace-nowrap'>
              predictable
            </div>
            <div
              class='md:text-xl text-base h-8 px-3 text-green rounded-[40px] bg-green/10 flex items-center justify-center whitespace-nowrap'>
              cheap
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class='text-green md:text-[28px] text-xl font-medium leading-tight'>
            Fashion is a struggle. bypassing norms and prejudices imposed by the community, and doing things that works
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class='bg-white min-h-screen py-28 px-5'>
      <p class='text-neutral-950 text-xl font-bold leading-tight'>First step</p>
      <p class='indent-10 md:text-[44px] text-[28px] leading-tight'>We are building stable and predictable income. <span
        class='text-neutral-300'>We just know how to make online sales profitable, and we are doing it in the first month.</span>
      </p>
      <div class='grid grid-cols-3 gap-4 w-full mt-8 h-[400px]'>
        <div class='flex flex-col gap-3 bg-[#F8F8F8] p-5 rounded-[20px]'>
          <svg width='24' height='24' viewBox='0 0 24 24' fill='none' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'>
            <circle cx='12' cy='12' r='12' fill='#008AFF' />
            <rect x='11' y='6' width='2' height='12' fill='#141414' />
          </svg>
          <p class='text-neutral-950 text-xl font-medium leading-tight'>
            Growth strategy and planning <span class='text-gray'>doubled sales after product
            assortment rearrangement</span>
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class='flex flex-col gap-3 bg-[#F8F8F8] p-5 rounded-[20px]'>
          <svg width='24' height='24' viewBox='0 0 24 24' fill='none' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'>
            <circle cx='12' cy='12' r='12' fill='#FFD203' />
            <rect x='9' y='6' width='2' height='12' fill='#141414' />
            <rect x='13' y='6' width='2' height='12' fill='#141414' />
          </svg>
          <p class='text-neutral-950 text-xl font-medium leading-tight'>
            Advertising management
            <span class='text-gray'>doubled sales after product assortment rearrangement</span>
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class='flex flex-col gap-3 bg-[#F8F8F8] p-5 rounded-[20px]'>
          <svg width='24' height='24' viewBox='0 0 24 24' fill='none' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'>
            <circle cx='12' cy='12' r='12' fill='#EE5C0A' />
            <rect x='7' y='6' width='2' height='12' fill='#141414' />
            <rect x='11' y='6' width='2' height='12' fill='#141414' />
            <rect x='15' y='6' width='2' height='12' fill='#141414' />
          </svg>
          <p class='text-neutral-950 text-xl font-medium leading-tight'>
            Revenue management,
            <span class='text-gray'>doubled sales after product assortment rearrangement</span>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class='bg-white min-h-screen py-28 px-5'>
      <p class='text-neutral-950 text-xl font-bold leading-tight'>Second step</p>
      <p class='indent-10 md:text-[44px] text-[28px] leading-tight'>We bring you data and speed. <span
        class='text-neutral-300'>It allows us to see more, control growth, and save tons of your time even on regular orders handling.</span>
      </p>
      <div
        class='mt-8 flex md:flex-row flex-col justify-between items-start gap-3 bg-[#F8F8F8] pl-5 pt-5 rounded-[20px] w-full h-[400px]'>
        <div class='max-w-xs'>
          <p class='text-2xl font-medium text-neutral-950 leading-tight'>Fully customisable personal dashboard</p>
          <p class='text-gray font-medium text-xl leading-tight'>You’ll knew everything about things you sell.
            From understanding the price</p>
        </div>
        <img src='/img_1.png' class='md:h-full' />
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class='bg-white min-h-screen py-28 px-5'>
      <p class='text-neutral-950 text-xl font-bold leading-tight'>Step three</p>
      <p class='indent-10 md:text-[44px] text-[28px] leading-tight'>We help you move to the next level.<span
        class='text-neutral-300'>
        Working on products, branding, pricing, and overall strategy. At this this time we start to understood what to do and what not, and may scale sales by the snap of fingers.</span>
      </p>
      <div class='grid grid-cols-4 gap-4 mt-8'>
        <div id='block-1' class='relative'>
          <div class='absolute top-[48%] left-0 bg-white rounded-r-[20px] w-2/3 text-xl font-medium leading-tight'>
            Vereja <span class='text-gray'>doubled sales after product assortment rearrangement</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div id='block-2' class='relative'>
          <div class='absolute bottom-2 right-0 bg-white rounded-r-[20px] w-2/3 text-xl font-medium leading-tight'>
            Vereja <span class='text-gray'>doubled sales after product assortment rearrangement</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div id='block-3' class='relative'>
          <div class='absolute top-0 left-0 bg-white rounded-r-[20px] w-2/3 text-xl font-medium leading-tight'>
            Vereja <span class='text-gray'>
            tripled sales in three months after rebranding and first marketing campaign
          </span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div id='block-4' class='relative'>
          <div class='absolute bottom-[48%] right-0 bg-white rounded-r-[20px] w-2/3 text-xl font-medium leading-tight'>
            Mirstores <span class='text-gray'>
             found out break-even point and fixed financial management
          </span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class='bg-white min-h-screen py-28 px-5'>
      <p class='text-neutral-950 text-xl font-bold leading-tight'>We charge commissions instead payments</p>
      <p class='indent-10 md:text-[44px] text-[28px] leading-tight'>allowing not to pay much that grow step by step<span
        class='text-neutral-300'>It allows you to use full potential of our team and pay less than when working with agency. Also, we both share risks.</span>
      </p>
      <div class='grid grid-cols-3 gap-4 w-full mt-8 h-[400px]'>
        <div class='flex flex-col justify-between bg-[#F8F8F8] p-5 rounded-[20px]'>
          <div class='flex flex-col gap-3'>
            <svg width='24' height='24' viewBox='0 0 24 24' fill='none' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'>
              <circle cx='12' cy='12' r='12' fill='#008AFF' />
              <rect x='11' y='6' width='2' height='12' fill='#141414' />
            </svg>
            <p class='text-neutral-950 text-xl font-medium leading-tight'>
              First 1-4 months <span class='text-gray'>doubled sales after product assortment rearrangement</span>
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class='flex flex-col gap-1'>
            <p class='text-2xl text-neutral-950 leading-tight font-medium'>15% for marketing</p>
            <p class='text-xl text-gray leading-tight font-medium'>no risks for start</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class='flex flex-col justify-between bg-[#F8F8F8] p-5 rounded-[20px]'>
          <div class='flex flex-col gap-3'>
            <svg width='24' height='24' viewBox='0 0 24 24' fill='none' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'>
              <circle cx='12' cy='12' r='12' fill='#FFD203' />
              <rect x='9' y='6' width='2' height='12' fill='#141414' />
              <rect x='13' y='6' width='2' height='12' fill='#141414' />
            </svg>
            <p class='text-neutral-950 text-xl font-medium leading-tight'>
              After 4 months,
              <span class='text-gray'>doubled sales after product assortment rearrangement</span>
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class='flex flex-col gap-1'>
            <p class='text-2xl text-neutral-950 leading-tight font-medium'>3% for platform</p>
            <p class='text-xl text-gray leading-tight font-medium'>additionally is included</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class='flex flex-col justify-between bg-[#F8F8F8] p-5 rounded-[20px]'>
          <div class='flex flex-col gap-3'>
            <svg width='24' height='24' viewBox='0 0 24 24' fill='none' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'>
              <circle cx='12' cy='12' r='12' fill='#EE5C0A' />
              <rect x='7' y='6' width='2' height='12' fill='#141414' />
              <rect x='11' y='6' width='2' height='12' fill='#141414' />
              <rect x='15' y='6' width='2' height='12' fill='#141414' />
            </svg>
            <p class='text-neutral-950 text-xl font-medium leading-tight'>
              Whenever you ready,
              <span class='text-gray'>doubled sales after product assortment rearrangement</span>
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class='flex flex-col gap-1'>
            <p class='text-2xl text-neutral-950 leading-tight font-medium'>Individually</p>
            <p class='text-xl text-gray leading-tight font-medium'>marketing and platform are included</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class='p-5 bg-white h-screen relative'>
      <video autoplay muted loop id='another' class='w-full h-full object-cover z-0 rounded-[20px]'
             poster='/img.webp'>
        <source src='/rage_longer_compressed.mp4' type='video/mp4' />
      </video>
      <div class='flex flex-col items-center absolute transform -translate-y-1/2 top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 z-50 w-full'>
        <p class='text-white md:text-[88px] text-[48px] leading-tight text-center md:max-w-4xl'>
          rage, rage against the dying of the light
        </p>
        <div class='flex flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4 text-white mt-24'>
          <a>x.com</a>
          <a>pm.me</a>
          <a>t.me</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
    #hero {
        height: 100vh;
    }

    #block-1 {
        background-image: url('/img_2.png');
        background-size: cover;
        background-position: center;
        height: 400px;
        border-radius: 20px;
    }

    #block-2 {
        background-image: url('/img_4.png');
        background-size: cover;
        background-position: center;
        height: 400px;
        border-radius: 20px;
    }

    #block-3 {
        background-image: url('/img_5.png');
        background-size: cover;
        background-position: center;
        height: 400px;
        border-radius: 20px;
    }

    #block-4 {
        background-image: url('/img_6.png');
        background-size: cover;
        background-position: center;
        height: 400px;
        border-radius: 20px;
    }
</style>